+----------+-----------+        +----------+-----------+
           |                               |
           v                               v
+----------------------+        +----------------------+
|   App workloads      |        | Observability stack  |
| deployment/rollout   |        | Prometheus/Grafana   |
+----------------------+        | Loki/Promtail        |
                                +----------------------+
